  "texts": [
    "To measure the isokinetic muscle strength, we used the Isokinetic Dynamometer (Biodex®, System 3 Pro, Biodex Corp., Shirley, NY, USA).",
    "The protocol used was the concentric unilateral mode for the extensor and knee-dominant flexor muscles.",
    "Patients were tested in a seated position with hip flexion.",
    "Stabilization straps were applied to the trunk, waist, and thigh.",
    "Evaluations of peak torque (three repetitions) and fatigue resistance (20 repetitions) were carried out at angular velocities of 90°s -1 and 180°s -1 of the dominant knee."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}